    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is preserved in pristine, showroom condition, exhibiting a level of care that borders on the fastidious. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained cabin, reflects an uncompromising standard of excellence. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a truly exemplary machine that defies its age. Performance remains as sharp as its aesthetic, ensuring a driving experience that is as rewarding as it is prestigious.",
      "price": 47500.0,
