      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and still has that new car feel. I\u2019m sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
