    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 naturally aspirated V8 era. The powerplant features an 8,400 RPM redline and ten individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power and immediate transient response. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including the installation of treated rod bearings and upgraded throttle actuators to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The 6-speed manual transmission provides a tactile connection to the variable M differential lock, while the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) retains its full range of damping coefficients. The chassis exhibits zero fatigue, with all subframe mounting points and suspension bushings in factory-original condition, preserving the car's peak torsional rigidity and kinematic precision.",
